data.description: This Drees Saxon is situated on a wooded, walkout homesite with relaxing pond views from the deck. Home features an open floor plan with 9' ceilings and luxury vinyl plank flooring. Kitchen has gray cabinets, quartz tops and tile backsplash. Additional features include a second floor laundry and a finished lower level rec room and half bath. Many upgrades! Timber Creek Views is conveniently located to shopping, dining and downtown Cincinnati.
